  { q: "What peptides does Strong Health prescribe?", a: "Our physicians prescribe pharmacy-grade peptides selected for your specific goals and labs. The most common protocols include BPC-157 and TB-500 for tendon, joint, and soft-tissue healing; CJC-1295 with Ipamorelin for body composition, sleep, and recovery; Tesamorelin for visceral (belly) fat; PT-141 for sexual desire and arousal; DSIP for deep-sleep architecture; and clinical-grade collagen peptides for connective tissue and skin. Every protocol is individualized — we don't use one-size-fits-all stacks." },
